quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,85,"IwoakukufunsazaMzimu.Ndiponena,“Ambuyewanga ndiye amene adziwa za iwo. Ndipo inu simudapatsidwe nzeru koma pang’ono pokha.”"
  17,86,"Ndithudi Ife tikadafuna, tikadakulanda chimene tavumbulutsa kwa iwe ndipo iwe siukadapeza wina aliyense wokuteteza kwa Ife m’malo mwako"
  17,87,"Kupatula chifundo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako, ndithudi ubwino wake pa iwe ndi waukulu zedi"
  17,88,"Nena, “Ngati anthu ndi majini akadagwirizana kubweretsa chofanana ndi Korani ino, iwo sakadabweretsa chofanana nayo ngakhale kuti iwo akadathandizana.”"
  17,89,Ndithudi talongosola kwa anthu mu Korani ino chitsanzo chilichonse. Komabe anthu ambiri akana choonadi ndi kukhala osakhulupirira
  17,90,"Iwo amati, “Ife sitidzakukhulupirira iwe mpaka pamene utatitumphutsira kasupe kuchokera pansi.”"
  17,91,“Kapena utakhala ndi munda wa tende ndi mphesa ndipo m’kati mwake utumphutse mitsinjeyaikulu.”
  17,92,“Kapenaugwetsemtambopaifemonga momwe udatilonjezera kapena utibweretsere Mulungu pamodzi ndi angelo pamaso pathu.”
  17,93,"“Kapena ukhale ndi nyumba yokongoletsedwa bwino kwambiri kapena ukwere kumwamba. Komabe ife sitidzakukhulupirira kukwera kwako mpaka pamene utatitsitsira ife Buku kuti tiziwerenga.” Nena, “Alemekezeke Ambuye wanga! Ndithudi ine sindine aliyense koma munthu amene watumizidwa ngati Mtumwi.”"